msgctxt "56_Rooftop Stalker"
msgid "*pant* *pant* *pant*"
msgstr "*jadea* *jadea* *jadea*"

msgctxt "68_Tanimura"
msgid "Man, you were a pain in the ass just now... Time to give that lady a call."
msgstr "De verdad, no pudiste haber sido un dolor tan grande en el culo hace un\\r\n"\n"momento... Hora de llamar a esa señora."

msgctxt "92_Tanimura"
msgid "Hello? Yes, this is Tanimura from the KPD. I caught your stalker."
msgstr "¿Hola? Sí, este es Tanimura del DPK. Atrapé a tu acosador."

msgctxt "152_Grateful Woman"
msgid "You did!?"
msgstr "¡¿Lo atrapaste?!"

msgctxt "164_Tanimura"
msgid "Yeah. He was shuffling around up here, doing... well, something shady."
msgstr "Sí. Él se estaba arrastrando por aquí, haciendo... bueno, algo turbio."

msgctxt "176_Rooftop Stalker"
msgid "Emi..."
msgstr "Emi..."

msgctxt "188_Emi"
msgid "Wait a second! This is my brother!"
msgstr "¡Espera un segundo! ¡Este es mi hermano!"

msgctxt "200_Tanimura"
msgid "Huh?"
msgstr "Uh, ¿y eso?"

msgctxt "260_Emi"
msgid "I'm sorry, Tanimura-san... It looks like my family was trying to protect me after they heard somebody was following me."
msgstr "Lo siento, Tanimura... Parece que mi familia estaba tratando de protegerme\\r\n"\n"después de escuchar que alguien me estaba siguiendo."

msgctxt "272_Tanimura"
msgid "You didn't have to be so damn sneaky about it!"
msgstr "¡No tenías que ser tan malditamente astuto al respecto!"

msgctxt "284_Emi's Brother"
msgid "But... I was afraid she was gonna yell at me for being overprotective..."
msgstr "Pero... Tenía miedo de que me gritara por ser sobreprotector..."

msgctxt "296_Emi"
msgid "I'm really sorry for causing this whole mess! Please accept this as a token of my apology."
msgstr "¡Lamento mucho haber causado todo este lío! Por favor, acepte esto como una\\r\n"\n"muestra de mis disculpas."

msgctxt "344_Tanimura"
msgid "Well, at least you have a family that loves you."
msgstr "Bueno, al menos tienes una familia que te ama."

msgctxt "356_Emi"
msgid "...Maybe a little too much."
msgstr "... Tal vez un poco demasiado."

msgctxt "368_Emi's Brother"
msgid "I just did what any caring older brother would do! I have no regrets!"
msgstr "¡Acabo de hacer lo que haría cualquier hermano mayor que se preocupa!\\r\n"\n"¡No me arrepiento!"

